Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:16.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:00.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be still, Straw Hat Luffy's shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your new master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to provide you with a voice and body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you may live as a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget all of your past relations\Nand become my obedient soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time! Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arise from 500 years of slumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How truly overawing!\NHe's a piece of art! A real devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This freak... is really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to say your last farewells?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is going to marry me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm disappearing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami vanished with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Belief Worth Begging to Live For!!\NBrook Defends His Afro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo ho ho ho, yo ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo ho ho ho, yo ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You refuse to quit even\Nafter I flung you outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I will continue to\Ncome back until you return to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All cower at the mere mention\Nof the swordsman Ryuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! You are my shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our bodies are worlds apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will come back to me!\NYou belong under my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Humming Swordsman isn't the\Nonly one here who knows our secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rottin' bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't die" is like our secret code.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna live in fear of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that after a person loses his shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he gets taken down this long staircase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Luffy got carried this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were chasing after him when Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Nami is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he wants to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll save her when we come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the more reason to hurry to Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wake up Straw Hat and the\Nguys and recover their shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the island is infested\Nwith zombies. That won't be easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of zombies,\Nhow did you take them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That skeleton taught us how. We used this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, guys, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is it?\N--The zombies' weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw how effective it was in my\Nbattle against this spider monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:08:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is their weakness? What exactly is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies have a weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can purify them if we\Nstuff salt into their mouths, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what exactly was that\Nmonstrous roar that came from upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously! We followed that sound here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Luffy's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you all about what we saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short, we're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it coming! He still wants more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much does a Special Zombie eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to consume\Neverything on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really stuffs his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumacy, why were you\Nharboring the pirates? Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk! You're so not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mini-Shallot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been feeding me and I\Ndon't even know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Course, the quantity bites and the food's nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it, Special Zombie!\NDon't step out of bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think gifted us\Nwith the ability to move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so rude to the ruler\Nof Thriller Bark if I were you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday the master is going\Nto become the King of the--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry! He told me to say all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude! Don't sell a friend out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry! I want more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring him more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's gobbled up nearly\Nall of the food on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're storing food in the\Ntreasure room in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to serve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Cindry-chan!\NAlways prepared for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Great!\N--I'm impressed that you set\Naside emergency rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But if you give that to Oars,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it defeats the point of the emergency rations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we completely run out of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not nice, Cindry-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyoro, Nin, Bao! Run over to\NHogback's mansion and get the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on it, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lend a helping hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let those pirates find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for the Humming Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If these guys could remove\Nthe spider monkey's shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're super bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the pirates?! The Humming Swordsman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I dropped this,\Nbut here it is! It's the basement key.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This leads to the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haul the stuff back up--all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feed him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This batch is actually pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A salted fish is somewhere in that pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he eats it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's salted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Special Zombie eats that, its shadow will--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, the master\Nis going to let us have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find it before he does!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish... Where is the fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Perona-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it! Don't say anything, Kumacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish! Fish! Fish! Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fish looks mighty yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't think you'll find it to\Nyour liking, Special Zombie-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sort of thing I\Nhave to find out for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Do you want\Nto get eaten along with the fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, don't let him eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are you guys getting\Nbetween me and my fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-We thought this might taste better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dried meat! Yeah, it's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving after all that hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll help myself to some fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shhh! Hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Oars! Five hundred years ago,\Nyou left behind countless legends
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as an infamous villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just now, I resurrected you in\Nmodern times to serve as my subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Subordinate"? Forget it! I have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of a zombie like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room is cramped and boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll set sail and travel\Nonce around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A voyage around the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This special freezer is encased in\Na super thick wall made of steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't put a dent in--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rottin' bad! Oars has gone outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. I could have\Nsworn my arm could stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to disgrace yourself by crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Anything but my afro! Anything but my afro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you beg me to spare\Nyour life, just like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not how it will go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mustered the courage to strike\Ndown those scary-looking zombies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they got right back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have some sort of weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I won't get my shadow back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I find my zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it off, zombies have\Nhorrendously scary faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the guys got purified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This picky eater just had\Nto grill the fish with salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--The idiot! He must have been new.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He grilled the fish with salt...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be the zombies' weakness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bastard! We stole your shadow\Nthe other day, Skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which zombie did you stuff my shadow into?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't answer, I'll scatter\Nfish all across the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fish"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you scatter them around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, that's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it couldn't possibly be salt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? "Salt"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-So what if you s-s-scatter that around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies really are insanely scary!\NI hate nighttime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jeez... It was just a grasshopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gave me a fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's dangerous for me to\Nbe out during daylight hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus it's easy for enemies to find me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it! I'll sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm scared, singing can\Nserve as a good distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful not to look at the\Nzombies' faces as I swiftly purify them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bound to run into my shadow eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that song coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's humming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal? What is\Nhappening on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He appears out of the darkness while humming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scary-looking swordsman\Nis searching for his shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's wiped out practically\Nall of the Soldier Zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perona-sama, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it! Don't wake me up, Kumacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last we meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he so strong? Isn't this\Nzombie supposed to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep up!\NAnd here we use the same style!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will end the same no matter\Nhow many times you come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would like to increase\Nyour speed somewhat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall cut that troublesome afro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't! At the very least,\Nplease leave my afro alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything but my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're my shadow, why don't you\Nunderstand how important this afro is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time has stopped for my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it would never grow back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What of it? I have forgotten\Nall about the days I served you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My current masters are\NMoria-sama and Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A skeleton that treasures its afro\Nis nothing short of ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please stop! Anything but my afro!\NAnything but my afro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything but my afro!\NNot my afro! Not the 'fro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a dirty move!\NAre you not ashamed of yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you will! There is a reason\Nwhy I cannot afford to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are most pathetic, former master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry. I admit defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to die, it would affect me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the epitome of disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While waiting for my chance to return,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have spent these past five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.76,0:22:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...growing stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:22:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better be ready to hold the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. We can start whenever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a lovely bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to start right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her dressed and bring\Nher to the ceremony hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.46,0:23:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That right? So that skeleton\Nhelped you out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That punk said he's endured these past\Nfifty years to keep a promise with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.23,0:23:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whale friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A whale...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Man's Promise Never Dies!!\NTo the Friend Waiting Under the Distant Sky!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
